                            <comment id="17937076" author="JIRAUSER288438" created="Thu, 20 Mar 2025 09:59:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi guys, Could some one please help review this simple PR.&lt;br/&gt;
The philosophy of the change is similar to what is being done with &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/hive/blob/master/llap-server/src/java/org/apache/hadoop/hive/llap/io/encoded/OrcEncodedDataReader.java#L241&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;OrcEncodedDataReader&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br/&gt;
The change is to simply use jobconf for initializing the FileSystem in &lt;em&gt;SerDeEncodedDataReader&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;VectorDeserializeOrcWriter&lt;/em&gt; as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
